
Greenie Linux (or just Greenie) is a computer operating system based on the popular Linux distribution Ubuntu. Unlike Ubuntu, Greenie is created for users in Slovakia and the Czech Republic. Greenie was founded on 14 September 2007 and currently it is the only distribution from Slovakia.

==Aim==

The main goal is to provide an easy-to-use operating system for use at home and as a live CD for different tasks.http://distrowatch.com/table.php?distribution=Greenie 

